imdb.plot outline: Relationship advice with a comic twist! Thanks for finding us! Is It Normal Or Not is a spin off of my Internet radio show "The G* Spot" on HotMix106.com. The questions featured are actual questions I received from my listeners, and I thought it would be fun to have some of my friends answer them as well. This channel is strictly for comedic purposes and, although tamer than some, we can be vulgar at times. We discuss dating, relationships, "unique" interests, body parts, and we drop an F*bomb every once in a while. It is NOT intended for minors or those easily offended by "adult" humor and topics.
imdb.title: Is It Normal or Not
akas: Is It Normal or Not (United States)
